"value takes precedence over that specified via @code{runtime-directory-"
"size}."
msgstr ""

#. type: item
#: guix-git/doc/guix.texi:26714
#, no-wrap
msgid "@code{runtime-directory-size} (type: maybe-non-negative-integer)"
msgstr ""

#. type: table
#: guix-git/doc/guix.texi:26717
msgid ""
"Set the size limit, in bytes, on the @env{XDG_RUNTIME_DIR} runtime directory"
" for each user who logs in."
msgstr ""

