msgstr ""

#. type: table
#: guix-git/doc/guix.texi:28154
msgid ""
"List of additional keys and values to include in the PostgreSQL config file."
"  Each entry in the list should be a list where the first element is the "
"key, and the remaining elements are the values."
msgstr ""

#. type: table
#: guix-git/doc/guix.texi:28160
msgid ""
