#. type: table
#: guix-git/doc/guix.texi:32164
msgid ""
"This option is specified using "
"@uref{https://www.openssl.org/docs/apps/ciphers.html#CIPHER-LIST-FORMAT, "
"OpenSSL cipher list notation}."
