"List of mount options.  Some options are simple flags, such as ro, noexec, "
"nosuid, etc.  These may be expressed as strings or symbols.  Other options "
"also accept a value.  These are expressed as pairs of @code{(option .  "
"value)}.  @code{option} may be a string or symbol, as with flags.  "
"@code{value} may be a string, symbol, or number.  Example: @code{(ro (errors"
" .  remount-ro) noexec)}"
msgstr ""

