#. type: Plain text
#: guix-git/doc/guix.texi:38047
msgid ""
"The @acronym{WSDD, Web Service Discovery daemon} implements the "
"@uref{http://docs.oasis-open.org/ws-dd/discovery/1.1/os/wsdd-"
"discovery-1.1-spec-os.html, Web Services Dynamic Discovery} protocol that "
"enables host discovery over Multicast DNS, similar to what Avahi does.  It "
