#, no-wrap
msgid "home-mcron-service-type"
msgstr ""

#. type: defvar
#: guix-git/doc/guix.texi:51027
msgid ""
"This is the type of the @code{mcron} home service, whose value is a "
"@code{home-mcron-configuration} object.  It allows to manage scheduled "
"tasks."
