"produces messages like \"@samp{@var{pid} @var{name}: @var{message}\"} "
"(@pxref{Invoking mcron, Invoking,, mcron,GNU@tie{}mcron}).  Each message is "
"also prefixed by a timestamp by GNU Shepherd."
