#. type: table
#: guix-git/doc/guix.texi:51743
msgid "Longitude, when @code{location-provider} is @code{'manual}."
msgstr ""

#. type: item
#: guix-git/doc/guix.texi:51744
#, no-wrap
msgid "@code{dawn-time} (type: maybe-string)"
msgstr ""

#. type: table
#: guix-git/doc/guix.texi:51748
msgid ""
"Custom time for the transition from night to day in the "
"morning---@code{\"HH:MM\"} format.  When specified, solar elevation is not "
"used to determine the daytime/nighttime period."
msgstr ""

#. type: item
#: guix-git/doc/guix.texi:51749
#, no-wrap
msgid "@code{dusk-time} (type: maybe-string)"
msgstr ""

#. type: table
#: guix-git/doc/guix.texi:51752
msgid ""
"Likewise, custom time for the transition from day to night in the evening."
msgstr ""

#. type: table
#: guix-git/doc/guix.texi:51757
msgid ""
"Extra content appended as-is to the Redshift configuration file.  Run "
"@command{man redshift} for more information about the configuration file "
